general.name: seguetsObjSetAllDup
general.description: All the SEGUE-2 targeting information is contained in these files. The files each give the targets covered by a 1.49 deg radius area; each file is named for a faint/bright pair of plates covering that area. In general, one is better off consulting the target files stored within the SSPP target directory tree , unless there appears to be an inconsistency there.
